Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.30,0:00:03.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Targeting only long-haired women...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.05,0:00:05.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Attacking with a hammer...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.64,0:00:06.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:07.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Hammer Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.52,0:00:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With information from a witness...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.23,0:00:13.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His apparent residence and apartment was identified.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.86,0:00:18.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The detectives underwent a covert stakeout.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.03,0:00:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To avoid being exposed, they arranged a love scene, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.74,0:00:28.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was reported by Detective Chiba that three people had\Nsuccessively entered and exited the staked out apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:32.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first: A male express home delivery\Ncourier that came for a package.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.67,0:00:37.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The second: A bike delivery woman who\Ncame to fulfill a luggage shipment request.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.92,0:00:41.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The third: A pizza man delivering a pizza.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.84,0:00:42.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.72,0:00:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All three claimed to have not met the resident.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.89,0:00:50.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A memo that instructed, "I'm bedridden with a cold,\Nso let yourself in and complete your business..."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.18,0:00:51.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was waiting under the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.11,0:01:00.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This could have been a diversionary tactic utilized\Nby the Hammer Man to escape the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.36,0:01:04.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Operating under that assumption, we forced our way inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.24,0:01:06.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.91,0:01:10.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We discovered a man who had taken a serious blow to the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:13.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this guy the "Hammer Man"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.71,0:01:17.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And was it one of the three who visited the apartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.29,0:01:18.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That struck him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:21.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Among those three...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.63,0:01:25.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There may have been someone related to\None of the hammer Man's four victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.01,0:01:28.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, when we tried to confirm their identities...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.64,0:01:30.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We learned that all three had already been released.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.31,0:01:34.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While investigating the room alongside the police...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.23,0:01:37.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came across several points of doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.77,0:01:39.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While the pizza receipt was found inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.65,0:01:42.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those for the bike and express service\Ndeliveries were nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.53,0:01:46.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The chargeable razor wasn't even plugged in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.49,0:01:49.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even the bathtub was remarkably clean...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.20,0:01:51.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.58,0:01:53.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's certainly something more to this case...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.66,0:01:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something beyond our imagination...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.96,0:02:02.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Love is eternal, labyrinths are mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.11,0:02:03.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saturday nights are for mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:06.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Hammer Man unexpected identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:08.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The captivating Deduction Queen, Sonoko, stages her entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.67,0:02:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:13.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While I was inspecting the washing machine and dryer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found this glove mixed in with the clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:14.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should forensics be able to link these blood\Nstains with those of the victim from last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:16.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can conclude that the man found collapsed here is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:18.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed the Hammer Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:23.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, if we could just find something left\Nbehind by the Hammer Man's attacker...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:25.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be a great clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.61,0:04:27.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:32.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These clothes were in the washing machine and dryer, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.36,0:04:33.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:36.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why aren't there any here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:38.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Any underwear or socks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.95,0:04:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:43.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are T-shirts, sweatshirts, towels and the like, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.83,0:04:46.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he threw them out after one use?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:51.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I once wore the same underwear for a week while on a stakeout.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.26,0:04:53.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Instead of washing them, I just threw them out...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:55.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stakeout...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:59.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were trying to appear as lovers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it wouldn't be so obvious you were on a stakeout, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:03.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:04.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What else did you have in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:06.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:09.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:10.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:15.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiba, you've been on a stakeout with Satou-san before, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:16.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:17.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two or three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.53,0:05:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And during those times... Did anything happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:21.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:23.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there wasn't, nevermind...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:26.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:28.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The time I was pretending to be Satou-san's boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satou-san seems to do it quite often, so\Nher identity as an officer remains secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.09,0:05:36.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In my case, after she made me do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.22,0:05:39.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't concentrate on the stakeout anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:41.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me — you too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.93,0:05:42.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:44.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will never forget it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:46.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That soft feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That soft feeling!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.69,0:05:50.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:52.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.11,0:05:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A hot one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:56.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:05:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.33,0:06:00.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:01.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.16,0:06:05.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We would like to take Conan-kun home soon, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.87,0:06:06.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:08.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Conan-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave the Hammer Man to us police.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.88,0:06:12.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.38,0:06:16.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, that man carried out on a stretcher\Nwas also attacked by the Hammer Man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.22,0:06:18.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.05,0:06:20.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one carried out was the Hammer Man himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:23.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was likely revenge carried out by\Nsomeone related to one of the victims...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:24.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:25.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:29.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought the Hammer Man was over 180 cm in height?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.65,0:06:31.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man that was just carried out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:34.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't even look as tall as 170 cm!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:36.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's an urban legend as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.99,0:06:39.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victims were all struck from behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:43.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And only saw the culprit from behind, as he was running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.58,0:06:46.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't be able to properly estimate his height.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.54,0:06:49.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The witness from last night was standing upright, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.38,0:06:52.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems he was drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.75,0:06:54.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An urban legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:58.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The unusually clean bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:00.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The unplugged electric razor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.68,0:07:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The absent toothbrush...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:03.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No underwear or socks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:04.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.60,0:07:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The note leading to the apartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:10.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The missing receipts for the express and bike deliveries...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:13.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.45,0:07:24.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a patch of leather attached to the tip of the left shoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.62,0:07:25.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other shoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.75,0:07:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the only shoe with a patch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:31.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.92,0:07:33.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.80,0:07:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there something wrong with the Hammer Man's shoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:39.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:41.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't the Hammer Man's shoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:45.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was no such thing to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.22,0:07:47.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing like a "Hammer Man," that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:49.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"There was no such thing as a 'Hammer Man' to begin with."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:55.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Things like the "Mouth-tearing Woman"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.69,0:07:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the "Human-faced Dog"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:08:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're merely embellished rumors that\Nend up as really scary stories, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.57,0:08:02.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And in the same vein...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:06.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Hammer Man running 100 meters in 11 seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.99,0:08:09.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And being over 180 cm tall...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:13.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All I'm saying is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:16.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are just exaggerated to scare everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "Mouth-tearing Woman" and "Human-faced Dog"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.84,0:08:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really know some pretty old stories, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.22,0:08:25.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard it from my school teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:27.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But see, Conan-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.22,0:08:30.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unlike the "Mouth-tearing Woman" and the "Human-faced Dog"...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:32.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Hammer Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:34.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has four confirmed victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:37.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't say he's fictitious...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.48,0:08:43.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That only tells you there's a bad person that is\Nattacking long-haired women with a hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.49,0:08:45.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you don't know if it's really the Hammer Man, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.20,0:08:50.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's called the Hammer Man precisely because he uses a hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:53.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you mean to say he didn't actually use a hammer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:55.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I mean is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:56.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:08:59.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speak up if you have something to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That strange dance...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:07.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.98,0:09:11.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:14.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After hearing that keyword from Conan-kun, it finally hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:18.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fact that we have been artfully manipulated to dance...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:23.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the urban legend of the Hammer Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:26.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deduction Queen Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.49,0:09:30.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, why does she seem exactly like Sleeping Kogorou?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you expect?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:33.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Compared to Mouri-san, the extent of her leaning is different...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.88,0:09:40.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, say, Sonoko-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the Hammer Man is merely an urban legend...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you explain the guy that was knocked out in this apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can only reason that one of those three who visited this apartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:55.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Decided to exact their revenge on the Hammer Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:59.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Try recalling and considering carefully...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The order in which those three entered, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The purpose for which they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.95,0:10:06.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.53,0:10:07.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.91,0:10:12.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A stout express home delivery man who was about 180 cm tall...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:16.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A short bike delivery woman who was about 160 cm tall...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And a thin pizza delivery man about 170 cm tall, in that order.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.46,0:10:24.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason all three came inside was...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:26.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A memo under the door read...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:31.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'm bedridden with a cold, so let\Nyourself in and complete your business."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:34.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And when it comes to the memo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.31,0:10:38.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should already be aware that only the home\Ndelivery courier that came first could place it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:39.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.56,0:10:43.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should also be aware that the only ones able to\Ndispose of the bike and express delivery receipts...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would be the two who appeared after the first\Nman — the bike courier and pizza carrier, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:51.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.66,0:10:53.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why we've been troubled until now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.91,0:10:57.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe it will become consistent should\Nwe consider it from this perspective...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.75,0:11:01.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if we suppose the one who placed\Nthe memo and disposed of the receipts...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:03.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was the Hammer Man in this apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:07.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, he might have been the one to put the memo there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.26,0:11:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what reason would the Hammer Man\Nhave for throwing away the receipts?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:15.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was to prevent us from promptly contacting\Ntheir employers to confirm their identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.56,0:11:20.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Considering they planned to switch\Nplaces with him from that point onward.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.73,0:11:21.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:23.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Switch places"? Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:27.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean to say the Hammer Man\Nswitched places with one of those three?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.40,0:11:29.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:31.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to switch places...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:35.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He called for express home delivery, bike delivery, and a pizza delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:36.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:39.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man found unconscious in the apartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:41.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is actually one of those three.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:43.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:45.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The people called over here by phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:46.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Followed the instructions on the memo under the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.63,0:11:50.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, when they consequently entered the apartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would strike them...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:56.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Help exchange their clothes for his uniform, pose it as a suicide...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.68,0:12:00.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then boldly exit out the front door of the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:02.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.31,0:12:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The express home delivery man that arrived\Nfirst can be eliminated as a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.90,0:12:10.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His physique is clearly far different from\Nthe man knocked out in the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.20,0:12:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's also unable to dispose of the\Nbike delivery receipt that came later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:17.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:20.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The pizza carrier is without a doubt the Hammer Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.08,0:12:23.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the fact that he hasn't returned to the shop further supports this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:25.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.21,0:12:26.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cordon off the area immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.84,0:12:28.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have to apprehend the pizza delivery man—\N\N{\alpha&HFF&\t(810,811,\alpha&H00&)}My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:30.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't you had enough dancing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:31.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.76,0:12:36.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just now, when I heard about the state of the\Napartment from Conan-kun, I instantly knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:37.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The true face of the Hammer Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.06,0:12:39.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The state of the apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:42.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The unusually clean bathroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:46.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The chargeable electric razor that was unplugged...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the missing toothbrush.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.69,0:12:53.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also mentioned that there were no\Nunderwear or socks among the clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:56.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you draw from that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:58.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:13:00.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cleaning the bathroom and removing the toothbrush...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:05.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were both acts to erase all traces that\Nthey had been living here all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The chargeable electric razor remained unplugged because...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:11.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't in use.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.34,0:13:16.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the reason there were no underwear or socks in the laundry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:18.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was to hide their gender.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.68,0:13:20.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should understand now, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:21.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:24.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, the Hammer Man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:31.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:32.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Hammer Man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:36.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That bike courier woman!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.57,0:13:37.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Underwear is obvious, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:43.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But even for the socks, which are usually small, they had to be hidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.37,0:13:46.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was all to conceal the fact that a woman was living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:50.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While it's true the attacker has always\Nbeen referred to as the "Hammer Man"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:54.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None of the victims ever identified the culprit as male.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:13:57.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was probably the media that assigned that name to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:14:00.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, the weapon being a hammer does have a violent precedent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:04.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And any moniker ending with "man" is always memorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.44,0:14:05.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:07.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though they said the one living here was male...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.98,0:14:10.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They also said he brought his girlfriend to live here as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.07,0:14:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:14.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who actually stopped coming was the man...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.57,0:14:17.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While the woman continued to stay in the apartment, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:22.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once you look at the shoe Conan-kun found\Nthat had a strip of leather attached to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:23.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It all becomes clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:29.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What it is is a shift pad, used for protecting\Nthe toe from the motorcycle's shift pedal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:32.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That shoe was the only one of its kind in the shoe cabinet...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:36.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And judging from the fact there were none others like it inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:41.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shoe doesn't belong to the bike delivery\Nwoman that's staying here, but instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.89,0:14:44.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It belongs to the true delivery man that was attacked here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:51.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's likely that she decided to take her feminine\Nclothes and shoes along with her underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were probably put in the daypack she used for the delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.36,0:15:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chances are, you'll find the pair of thick-soled boots inside\Nthat she used to gain the height of a male for her attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If she weren't wearing those boots that were popular in the past...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The drunk witness wouldn't have been able to keep up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:11.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.79,0:15:15.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's so, why didn't the pizza carrier return to the shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.97,0:15:20.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's highly probable he was knocked unconscious\Nby the culprit and locked away somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.05,0:15:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should he not return, the police would naturally suspect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.18,0:15:25.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.60,0:15:27.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Organize a cordon immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For now, I'm not sure it's necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.69,0:15:33.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if we don't hurry, she'll get the bike and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:35.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If her intent was to use a motorcycle...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:39.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't have left this shoe equipped with a shift pad here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.36,0:15:40.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:42.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She planned to waste no time getting out of her jumpsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.37,0:15:46.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, it wouldn't be easy to ride in a taxi with it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:50.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While it's true that changing in a bathroom would be ideal...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:53.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She would garner too much attention in a family restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.59,0:15:57.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And make it more likely someone would remember\Nher normal clothes and face without cosmetics.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.38,0:16:00.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for a bathroom that would make that avoidable...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.18,0:16:02.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A park bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's a nearby park...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.31,0:16:06.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd have to be where the incident happened last night, Beika Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:08.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.02,0:16:09.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's being investigated as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stupid man...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Believing such a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.57,0:16:22.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:24.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that park back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:27.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a bathroom stall that wouldn't open,\Nso would you mind coming along with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:31.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just concerned because this was\Nthe site of a Hammer Man attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:33.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.46,0:16:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not seeing that stall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.59,0:16:41.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, I just have to get out of this jumpsuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:46.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get out of this park...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:50.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And find myself in a place where the\Neyes of the stupid police can't reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:53.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:56.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm with the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:17:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are aware an incident occurred here just last night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.99,0:17:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there something in the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:07.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:10.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if it has anything to do with the case, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.16,0:17:13.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back in the inner stall, there's a collapsed man lying there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:19.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:21.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go ahead and call for my subordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:26.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you will cooperate, please come along and answer some questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:28.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be my pleasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've heard all about you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.31,0:17:36.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss "Hammer Man."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:38.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:43.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And with that, the Hammer Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:44.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.70,0:17:46.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Hammer Woman, was safely apprehended.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:50.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The peculiar urban legend that spread so suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.41,0:17:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Came to an end before greeting the next generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.58,0:17:57.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her motive for the crimes was unwarranted\Nresentment for the man who left her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.34,0:18:00.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for targeting long-haired women...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:04.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was simply the type her boyfriend starting seeing after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:07.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the witness found out where she lived...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:12.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She decided not just to run but to make\Nthat man out to be the real culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:16.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was surrounded by the police much faster than she expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.77,0:18:19.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And resorted to foolish decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.23,0:18:23.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were a huge help back there, Sonoko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.94,0:18:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was as remarkable as a Sleeping Kogorou deduction!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:29.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially when you said, "Haven't you had enough dancing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:32.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were like a real Deduction Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.41,0:18:34.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.83,0:18:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:37.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not the details...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:39.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.71,0:18:41.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you too, Conan-kun—thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:44.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.17,0:18:45.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How far did it get?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:47.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How "far" did what get?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.63,0:18:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:50.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With Satou-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.43,0:18:54.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hasn't it been a while since you started dating her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:56.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to discuss it with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:58.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.56,0:19:01.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I pretended to be Satou-san's\Nboyfriend on that one stakeout?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.90,0:19:04.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not upset or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, we just held hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.49,0:19:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But wait, I remember you saying something about a "soft feeling"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:16.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the feeling of her squeezing my hand so tightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:21.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, right after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was scared by the look she was using to glare at the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.17,0:19:25.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, just a little, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:27.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that was all?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:28.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:30.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't she do the same with you, Takagi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:32.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a stakeout, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:35.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, in my case...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:37.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.52,0:19:39.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:41.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A hot one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.31,0:19:43.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.86,0:19:44.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because it was me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.44,0:19:48.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because it was me, Satou-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.45,0:20:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've finally located the home of the suspect's\Nyounger brother in the murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:06.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's in Okucho-cho, District 3, second floor of the pachinko parlor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.09,0:20:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to our intel, the chances of him\Nmeeting with the suspect soon are high.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.22,0:20:14.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll need some of you on stakeout, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.51,0:20:18.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going with Satou, who has followed this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.27,0:20:20.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:22.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please select me, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:27.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's so unlike you to volunteer for a stakeout.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:29.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You weren't aware?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:31.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I actually really love stakeouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.07,0:20:33.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep your guard up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:37.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He may just be the brother, but they say he's merciless all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:37.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.66,0:20:39.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:40.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:41.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.08,0:20:43.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Be careful"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.38,0:20:49.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:50.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No movement, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.05,0:20:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Satou...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:54.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:58.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The name "Satou" is a pretty common one, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.14,0:21:00.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.98,0:21:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At least it's a good name, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.64,0:22:26.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Matsumoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.44,0:22:31.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm currently at Enba Harbor in pursuit of the serial killer suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.40,0:22:32.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.19,0:22:32.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.07,0:22:34.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.15,0:22:37.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stolen car's model and color match the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.91,0:22:40.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's proceeding to park now, and is the only one inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.45,0:22:43.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Confirming plate number now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.12,0:22:44.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shinjuku 5—
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.00,0:22:50.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Matsumoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.34,0:22:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.55,0:22:53.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whistling?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.60,0:23:04.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.14,0:23:04.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.98,0:23:08.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's whistling right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.06,0:23:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That tune!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.61,0:23:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He saw me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.24,0:23:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.74,0:23:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Respond, Matsumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:19.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.42,0:23:20.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.20,0:23:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent Matsumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.04,0:23:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.54,0:23:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seemed to be out of it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.25,0:23:30.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.71,0:23:33.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems I dozed off for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.00,0:23:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not go home and get some rest when you get a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.22,0:23:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As of late, you've been staying overnight\Nand not getting any rest, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.05,0:23:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing that can be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.47,0:23:47.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The expiration on the serial murder case is in one week.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.10,0:23:54.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even now, the hands on the clock are ticking.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.11,0:24:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.03,0:24:03.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are those two people who came forward right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.91,0:24:06.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the one who left this scar on my face...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.70,0:24:08.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The suspect from back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.35,0:24:32.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.69,0:24:34.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nickname
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.48,0:24:36.48,Signs,,0,0,0,,Look forward to the next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.50,0:24:36.34,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The amazing Deduction Queen, Sonoko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.00,0:24:38.77,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And the Dance Queen as well, you know.
